title: Table for one
description:
Our story tonight is called Table for one and its a story about a rainy afternoon watched from a favorite place. It’s also about an old radiator that hisses and bangs under the window, a meal that feels like love and enjoying the pleasure of your own company.

So get cozy and ready to sleep.

Buy the book:http://hyperurl.co/NothingMuchHappens

Get an autographed copy and other merch here: https://www.nothingmuchhappens.com/nmh-stuff 

Get our ad-free and bonus episodes here: https://nothingmuchhappens.supportingcast.fm
